quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  26,53,Ndipo Farawo adatumiza mithenga ku mizinda yonse
  26,54,“Ndithudi anthu amenewa ndi kagulu ka anthu ochepa.”
  26,55,“Ndithudi anthu amenewa atipsetsa mtima.”
  26,56,“Ife tonse tili tcheru.”
  26,57,Ndipo tidawachotsa m’minda ndi mu a kasupe
  26,58,Ndiponso m’chuma ndi m’malo alionse olemekezeka
  26,59,Kotero tidawapanga ana a Israyeli kukhala alowa m’malo a zinthu za anthu a Farawo
  26,60,"Pamene dzuwa linali kutuluka, iwo adalondoledwa ndi adani awo"
  26,61,"Ndipo pamene magulu awiriwa adaonana wina ndi mnzake, anthu a Mose adati, “Ndithudi atipeza.”"
  26,62,"Mose adati, “Iyayi. Ndithudi Ambuye wanga ali ndi ine ndipo adzanditsogolera.”"
  26,63,"Ndipo tidalamulira Mose kuti, “Menya madzi a m’nyanja ndi ndodo yako.” Ndipo nyanja idagawanika pakati, mbali iliyonse idali ngati phiri lalikulu"
  26,64,Ndipo anthu a Farawo tidawayandikitsa ndi nyanja ija
  26,65,Ndipo Ife tidapulumutsa Mose ndi onse amene adali ndi iye
  26,66,Ndipo tidamiza ena
  26,67,Ndithudi mu ichi muli phunziro komabe anthu ambiri sakhulupirira ayi
  26,68,Ndithudi Ambuye wako! Iye ndiye Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha
  26,69,Ndipo afotokozere nkhani za Abrahamu